Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=28}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rob Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:11.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então eles realmente vão se livrar do Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo aqui, cara do pombo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é uma ilha do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós é que estamos fora de lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem liga pra isso agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo pro andar de cima, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que saco!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:34.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E tem a Jewelry Bonney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.31,0:00:40.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas não os ataque, Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:44.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora que o Chapéu de Palha é um Imperador,\Nprecisamos de autorização dos superiores pra agir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tem razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Quatro Imperadores vêm com aliados.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:51.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma briga pode levar a uma guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Reportem aos Marinheiros imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.83,0:00:54.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhora!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei muito bem que não deveria lutar com ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pega a Bonney, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que horror!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa garota...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente acabou de ver ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, cuida dela!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:25.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:32.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que vamos precisar\Nda expertise do Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiquem fora disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é assunto do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:52.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela nos deu um monte de comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Chapéus de Palha estão em Egghead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá vendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As coisas estão se complicando de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:45.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Será que o Vegapunk descobriu\Na missão da CP0?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:49.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim. É por isso que tiveram que forçar a entrada...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é basicamente uma declaração de guerra...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:59.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aqueles moleques deviam ter nos consultado antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:04.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se o Vegapunk tem o Chapéu de Palha do lado dele,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,podemos sofrer perdas tremendas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê o Kizaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá a caminho de Egghead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:16.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pra missão que planejamos\Ncom bastante antecedência.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:20.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Digam ao Lucci pra esperar a Marinha chegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:25.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não permitam que ele lute com o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Invasores! Evacuem imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evacuem imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pombo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos lutar mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é debochado como sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso me irrita muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:39.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não é o único que ficou mais forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Rob Lucci sempre foi assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para, Lucci! Não temos autorização!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que velocidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como isso é raro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:03.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A maioria dos usuários de zoan despertos\Nperde a personalidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai se ferrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Calma, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pensa na sua posição!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso pode causar um alvoroço enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Shaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O guerreiro de branco apareceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O de verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas a gente acabou de ver ele lá embaixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não consigo acreditar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:04.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me diz! Que transformação é essa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pela qual ele passou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós também não sabemos muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é a Fruta Gomu Gomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa fruta não existe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:22.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,em nenhuma das antigas enciclopédias de frutas do diabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não! Mesmo que você diga isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá sempre dizendo "Gomu Gomu."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que figura magnífica!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:39.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa aparência dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,se parece com um ser da literatura antiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é a cara de um deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um deus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabe, um idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De fato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:08:00.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O tolo e cômico Guerreiro da Libertação\Nque traz sorrisos a todas as pessoas!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Também conhecido como...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:07.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o Deus do Sol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:07.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nika? Nunca ouvi esse nome antes...
Comment: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nika?
Comment: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I've never heard that name before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é de se estranhar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele foi apagado da história.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas ele existe enquanto as pessoas desejarem sua presença!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todas as coisas são trazidas a\Neste mundo por causa dos desejos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por exemplo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,as frutas do diabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As frutas do diabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:41.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,são manifestações das aspirações\Ndas pessoas pela evolução humana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Eu quero ser assim."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Eu quero ser assado."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:49.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os diferentes poderes representam\Nos diversos futuros da humanidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E por isso, essa condição antinatural\Ntem um preço:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:57.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ser desprezado pelo mar, a mãe da natureza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os que possuem poderes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,cada um vive em realidades diferentes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:13.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,nascidas da imaginação de alguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa é minha teoria!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:26.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faz sentido nem perguntar se um deus existe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse mundo não é fascinante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:39.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esses caras... Não sabem\Nonde estão?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isso não é um parquinho pro\Ngoverno e piratas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hoje era pra ser minha folga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O que demorou tanto, Sentomaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí, Velho Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Cipher Pol é nossa aliada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Piratas são nossos inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devo lutar junto com a CP0?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não, hoje não, Sentomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O negócio é que a CP0 tá mirando em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:14.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preciso que você os expulse daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso vai me tornar um traidor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso que você faça uma escolha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sentomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lembre-se que você precisa pagar suas dívidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem te salvou...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,da pobreza...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,fui eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O que vai ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que pressão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai atacar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles possuem três seraphim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:52.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos prestes a ficar numa situação crítica!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, S-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Derruba um deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:11:00.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se mova, S-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:04.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem chance, Kaku!\NNós estamos em desvantagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se livre desses agentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recuar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:25.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos com problemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:26.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:31.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Sentomaru tem prioridade sobre nossos chips de autoridade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:32.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As ordens do pacifista são priorizadas\Ncom base em quem as emite.
Comment: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,The pacifista follow a hierarchy of authority
Comment: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,and their priorities depend on who issues the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro, os Cinco Anciãos têm a prioridade máxima.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O segundo é o Dr. Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O terceiro é Sentomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:56.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Portadores de chip de autoridade como nós são o quarto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não importa o que fizermos,\No Sentomaru tem a palavra final!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então temos que pedir\Naos Cinco Anciãos pra pará-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É inútil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles precisam ser comandados diretamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:16.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que sejam os Cinco Anciãos, o pacifista\Nnão aceita ordens por den den mushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E se parar pra pensar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,destruir os seraphim significa\Nprejuízo pro governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maldito Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele devia ter pensado antes de agir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Toupeira...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Levem o Chapéu de Palha e os outros\Npro foguete a vácuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:07.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles precisam chegar ao Frontier Dome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Hawk! S-Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Segurem os agentes da CP0!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:15.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, não acredito no que eu tô vendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:20.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquelas pessoas de pele mais escura parecem\Ncom os antigos Sete Guerreiros do Mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A semelhança é impressionante!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:27.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que fizeram clones de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Machado de guerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é minha arma, não meu nome,\Ne não aja tão feliz em me ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nós somos inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:46.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai ajudar o Velho Punk\Na sair daqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, ele me pediu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:50.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei se posso contar com você...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que você é um Imperador agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E esse seu visual é ridículo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistola de Dedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Machado de guerra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:17.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só precisava eliminar o comandante...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:21.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seraphim, obedeçam nossas ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te distraí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota...
Comment: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me subestime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu percebi e...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.40,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu achei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,que tinha bloqueado...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que persistente...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:08.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desmaia logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua autoridade é maior que a nossa,\Nentão enquanto você estiver consciente...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não conseguimos controlar os seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:26.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aurora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Chicote!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:41.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora é nossa chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, se apresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:55.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você quer salvar essa garota,\Nprecisamos ir logo ao Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu adoraria, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aonde você vai, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô girando demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se abriguem na fábrica!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:03.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os seraphim são imparáveis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não faz sentido brigarmos entre nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E eles ainda são crianças.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O potencial deles é aterrorizante.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual o problema?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O problema é esse poder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha o que o Jinbe pequeno tá fazendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não é o poder da Fruta Nada-Nada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fruta Nada-Nada?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:26.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o poder do meu irmão jurado\Nda Família Donquixote...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:35.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O poder do Senor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não podem existir duas frutas\Niguais nesse mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso quer dizer que ele morreu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu mano não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você percebeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:55.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse seu mano tá em Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá dizendo que duplicou a fruta do diabo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As frutas do diabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,podem ser feitas artificialmente\Nse forem do tipo zoan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, as frutas SMILE do Caesar são inaceitáveis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, ele que vá pro inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:30.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,As frutas SMILE são arriscadas demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:34.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No máximo, uma em cada dez pessoas\Nganha poder ao comer uma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:39.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo sem poder\Né forçado a sorrir o tempo todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:39.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que horrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só de ouvir esse nome já me dá ânsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, deixando isso de lado...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que todo tipo\Nde fruta pode ser replicado...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,com bastante dinheiro e tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas o despertar delas ainda é um mistério.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiz tudo que pude pra replicar\Nas do tipo logia, sem sucesso...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pras do tipo paramecia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,descobri que se eu conseguir\Nos elementos hereditários do usuário,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:27.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,posso criar uma infusão especial de sangue que,\Nquando administrada,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,permite que outra pessoa tenha o poder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o sangue que corre nos braços deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O sangue verde!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você fez seu próprio sangue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:52.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mero Mero no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:10.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os seraphim são o auge\Ndas minhas conquistas científicas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Ursus Shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pode-se dizer que eles são...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:30.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,a forma mais forte de humanidade já conhecida!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:33.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É por isso que os Sete\NGuerreiros foram abolidos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:37.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é louco por criar\Nalgo mais forte que eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:41.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles são essencialmente as armas da Marinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:41.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A criação deles representa uma ameaça pra nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Sentomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:21:59.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fiquem longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda tá...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:18.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fuja, Capitão Sentomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde foi seu amigo idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E ele não é meu amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala essa boca traiçoeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:39.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Soru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:48.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu peste!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.69,0:24:20.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aurora...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:34.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Foguete!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.41,0:24:39.87,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quão forte ele ficou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.63,0:24:43.80,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô quase...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:49.09,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,desmaiando!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.94,0:25:02.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por aqui! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.83,0:25:14.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito lento!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:20.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que não dá pra acelerar?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.92,0:25:22.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o foguete a vácuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:25.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Subam agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.13,0:25:27.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.26,0:25:30.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é uma Hancock gentil!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.18,0:25:32.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Valeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.30,0:25:33.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você ajudou muito!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.93,0:25:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-Insolência!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:38.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu só tô seguindo ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.35,0:25:46.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O foguete parte em um minuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.32,0:25:48.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.86,0:25:50.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se apresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.70,0:25:55.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah não!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.99,0:25:59.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por favor, não corram pra dentro do foguete.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.00,0:26:01.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.13,0:26:07.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Confio o Velho Punk a você!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.84,0:26:10.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beleza!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:12.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.76,0:26:16.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para! Vai pro outro lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.10,0:26:21.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As portas estão fechando.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.60,0:26:22.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por favor, tomem cuidado.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.82,0:26:35.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos tirá-lo da ilha...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.87,0:26:40.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.14,0:27:00.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Partindo agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.69,0:27:07.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca andei num–
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.49,0:27:18.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é impressionante!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.08,0:27:21.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde eu tô?! Cadê o Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.33,0:27:27.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu ainda posso lutar...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:29.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1420,1053)}O quê?! Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.09,0:27:30.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,590)}Esse é o Luffy!\NMuita coisa aconteceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.71,0:27:32.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,590)}Eu explico depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.46,0:27:33.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1420,1053)}Isso é ridículo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.93,0:27:38.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, acho que tô me acostuman– Não! Rápido demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.47,0:27:39.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca, médico de navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.76,0:27:40.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que rápido...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:43.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Até quando você vai ficar\Nassim, Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.15,0:27:51.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Partindo do Fabriophase\Ncom destino ao Labophase.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.20,0:27:57.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Duração do trajeto:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.49,0:27:59.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}trinta e dois segundos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.70,0:28:02.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chegamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.58,0:28:03.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.87,0:28:06.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todos os foguetes subsequentes estão cancelados.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.92,0:28:09.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Labophase, Egghead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.21,0:28:11.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Frontier Dome agora reforçado.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.79,0:28:13.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alerta de invasor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.30,0:28:14.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.63,0:28:20.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pesquisadores, por favor evacuem\Npra fábrica e selem o prédio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.27,0:28:28.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é admirável, de certa forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:34.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você cumpriu seu dever pelo Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:36.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,como guarda-costas dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.49,0:28:38.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.95,0:28:41.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é uma pena, Sentomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.12,0:28:45.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os Marinheiros mandaram esperarmos a chegada deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.45,0:28:47.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como eles podem levar isso tão de leve?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:50.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se esperarmos, ele vai fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:53.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles realmente estão tentando te matar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.34,0:28:56.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o cara mais inteligente do mundo, certo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.42,0:28:59.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seria prejuízo pro governo se você morresse!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.51,0:29:00.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim, suponho que sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.72,0:29:04.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas tente se colocar\Nno lugar dos superiores.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.93,0:29:10.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minhas invenções foram\Nbenéficas pro governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.73,0:29:14.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Inovações usando pedra-do-mar em tecnologia de navegação.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.48,0:29:16.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A produção de animais ciborgues.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.49,0:29:21.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Também estudei as frutas do diabo\Ne apliquei minhas descobertas com sucesso.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.95,0:29:24.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Criei armas humanas, os pacifista.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.83,0:29:27.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.91,0:29:30.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,completei os seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.67,0:29:36.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, se eu me voltasse contra vocês como\Na maior inteligência do mundo, e daí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.59,0:29:37.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.46,0:29:39.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu ficaria puto!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.38,0:29:42.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te mataria!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.01,0:29:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não "mata" ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.22,0:29:48.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não tenho a menor\Nintenção de me revoltar,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.56,0:29:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas aqueles cabeças-duras\Nacreditam firmemente que sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:56.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, é assim que as coisas são.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.27,0:29:58.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não fala como se fosse problema dos outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.32,0:30:03.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aí o seu grupo liderado por um\Ndos Quatro Imperadores apareceu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.57,0:30:05.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então deve ser o destino!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.91,0:30:06.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.58,0:30:09.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você vai embarcar no nosso navio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É muito bem-vindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.21,0:30:14.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.29,0:30:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha o General Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.09,0:30:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o Sunny... Olha ele também!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.55,0:30:23.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?! Ele vai embarcar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.38,0:30:24.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é uma responsabilidade enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.14,0:30:26.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupa, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.93,0:30:28.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu te protejo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.64,0:30:30.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô contando com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.60,0:30:32.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deem o melhor de si-{\i1}quasar{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.94,0:30:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.64,0:30:35.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então por que não solta nossos pés?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.15,0:30:37.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:40.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dra. Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.15,0:30:41.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah não!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.11,0:30:42.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.90,0:30:44.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos cuidar de você agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.03,0:30:48.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem pra tratar e consertar ela o mais rápido possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.49,0:30:50.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por trazê-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.79,0:30:52.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deixa ela com a gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.50,0:30:53.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, valeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.87,0:30:56.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, vocês! Cadê o Vegapunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:30:59.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que ele tá aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.80,0:31:01.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me digam!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.38,0:31:03.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Para com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.30,0:31:04.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se acalma um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.18,0:31:10.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então esse é o laboratório dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.43,0:31:14.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Massa!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.06,0:31:15.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha esse lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.19,0:31:18.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquele maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.23,0:31:21.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou fazer ele pagar!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.36,0:31:27.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bonney, aonde você vai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.79,0:31:35.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se a resposta do Vegapunk ao meu pedido\Npra mudar meu pai de volta...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.46,0:31:39.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,foi aqueles insetos...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.17,0:31:45.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eu não tenho escolha senão matá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.17,0:31:47.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Você só tá descontando nele...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.05,0:31:50.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.64,0:31:52.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para, Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.18,0:31:54.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Bonney!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.91,0:32:10.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossos chips de autoridade voltaram a funcionar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.78,0:32:13.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os seraphim agora são nossos.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.83,0:32:15.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A maré virou!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.33,0:32:18.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu derrubei um dos satélites.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.00,0:32:24.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Contando com o corpo principal\Ndo Vegapunk, restam seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.21,0:32:27.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.22,0:32:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.55,0:32:31.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,aquele sistema de defesa é formidável.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.51,0:32:36.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar nem uma formiga sair dessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.52,0:32:38.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Destruam todos os navios aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.27,0:32:40.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bloqueiem todas as rotas de fuga também!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.36,0:32:43.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não os deixem escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:59.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então os Chapéus de Palha estão do lado do Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.17,0:33:03.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso dá a ele um meio de fuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.59,0:33:08.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas provavelmente...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.14,0:33:15.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não vai sair como ele imagina.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.85,0:33:20.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Procedam como planejado.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.77,0:33:23.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enviem todos os navios disponíveis...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.19,0:33:27.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,para Egghead.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=29}===============================DIALOGUE============================
